_sText:
cs_gmancity has now received a full sized update to the map! Featuring new routes, decals, fog, visual improvements, sound ambience, detail, and a general quality of life improvement. The map will also no longer be called gmancity, now renamed to GGcity. The map has also received a gamemode update, it's now a proper hostage map. Enjoy :)

STORY:
 Terrorists have made themselves known in the streets & alleyways of GGcity, causing chaos left and right, ultimately making the place deserted, with a few kidnapped hostages. The only people that remain are the terrorists & a bunch of CT's ready to stop them. Will they survive?
